data.description: Welcome to this stunning custom-built house located in the desirable Springview Farms neighborhood of Bluffdale City. This spacious home offers luxury and comfort with its 6 bedrooms and 5 bathrooms, spanning across 4,439 square feet of living space. Situated on a generous .31-acre lot, this property provides ample space for outdoor activities and enjoyment. As you enter, you'll be captivated by the meticulous craftsmanship and high-end finishes throughout. The main level showcases a perfect blend of rustic and modern elements, featuring solid alder cabinets and hardwood flooring. The recently finished basement adds an additional touch of contemporary style to this already impressive home. The well-designed floor plan includes a bonus room above the garage, complete with a 3/4 bathroom, offering flexibility for use as a guest suite, office, or recreational area. The fully finished basement provides even more living space and versatility to suit your needs. Step outside and discover the expansive outdoor covered deck and patio, providing an ideal setting for entertaining guests or simply relaxing while enjoying the breathtaking views of the Kennecott Copper Mine and the picturesque Salt Lake Valley. Parking will never be an issue with the oversized 2-car garage and an additional 3rd RV garage featuring a large 10-foot door, perfect for storing recreational vehicles, boats, or other toys. The garage is fully finished and includes a heater for added convenience. Conveniently located near the Jordan Parkway River Trail, Redwood Road, and I-15, this property offers easy access to a variety of nearby amenities and attractions. The upcoming "The Point" complex promises to bring even more excitement and entertainment options to the area. Residents of this community benefit from the proximity to Summit Academy Private School, ensuring quality education opportunities for students. Additionally, the front runner and trax station are just a few miles away, making commuting a breeze. With no gated community restrictions and an affordable HOA fee of $75 per month, this property provides the perfect balance of privacy and convenience without compromising on quality. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this exceptional Steve Dailey Construction home in the sought-after Springview Farms neighborhood. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of luxury living in Bluffdale City.
